      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AARIELLA'S GIRL (3) has a superb record at this track and trip, unbeaten so far from three starts. Hit the frame latest (19.49) when second at Hobart in a Grade 4. Looks suited and should go close. KIWI ICE CUBE (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Hobart over 340m (19.46). Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. GINGER RUSH (2) turned in a moderate effort last time when seventh at Hobart over 340m behind Rojo Jojo (20.35) in a Grade 4. Likely to be about the money. YES EILEEN (5) has strong credentials over this journey.",
